I'm actually getting Tahm soon and i'm gonna have a level 9 train me to do clutch saves because he regularly goes too deep, lol. Braum I can see myself getting good with if I can get rid of my "poke always and beat face all the time mentality" and Taric is good fun but cooldowns  limit such a fabulous man, so i'm gonna see if I can get a weird cooldown reduc build til people start showing that they can stop going in at 25% health.

